  mySprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f6f8c12f37d09bc4abcef0ca6e86fb0e, type: 3}
  OutcomeRef: 1
  myName: percussion
  myDescription: "Your energy is the most chaotically entertaining one known to humanity.
    The soul of every group, you are the person that agrees to an adventure before
    there is any plan and somehow comes out victorious. You bring zest and vitality
    wherever you go, keeping everyone on their toes. Others might find themselves
    relying on you in unexpected situations. When the moment matters, your timing
    is flawless, as if you kept track of everything all this time (you did and made
    it look effortless). You\u2019re spontaneous, lively, and impossible not to smile
    around. Others might plan ahead, but you? You feel when the moment is right,
    and you nail it every time."
